org.sql: SELECT devices.* FROM devices WHERE devices.user_id = "$1" AND devices.token IS NULL AND devices.platform = "$2" AND devices.consumer_app_id = "$3" LIMIT "$4"

rewrites.sql: SELECT devices.* FROM devices WHERE devices.user_id = "$1" AND False AND devices.platform = "$2" AND devices.consumer_app_id = "$3" LIMIT "$4"
